title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, Northeast]
description: Oak trees cluster together around a thin path leading out in three directions.  They weave a dark canopy of leaves overhead, blocking the light of the stars overhead.  The trees appear to thin out somewhat toward the west.

Oak trees cluster together around a thin path leading out in three directions.  They weave a dark canopy of leaves overhead, blocking the light of the sun overhead.  The trees appear to thin out somewhat toward the west.
